{"title":"Best Apple deals: Mac, iPad, AirPods, Apple Watch, and more","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/541154/apple-deals.html","date":1701788745000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>Whether you’re looking to gift an Apple product or just pick one up for yourself, we’ve scoured the web for the best prices on everything from Macs to MacBooks, iPads to iPhones, Apple Watches to Apple TVs, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are wondering if Apple has sales, prepare to be disappointed. Apple rarely discounts its own products–even during its annual <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/672787/apple-black-friday.html\">Black Friday shopping event</a>, it traditionally elects to give out gift vouchers rather than reducing prices. It also offers <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/670705/how-to-get-an-apple-student-discount-at-apples-education-store.html\">year-round discounts to students</a>, including a <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/673191/apple-back-school-sale.html\">Back To School event</a> where students can get up to $150 in gift cards when purchasing certain Apple products. There’s also the <a href=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=1-1-541154-1-0-0&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/refurbished\" target=\"_blank\">Apple Refurbished Store</a> where you can sometimes grab a bargain. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>But if you want a new Apple device right now, other stores often offer up Apple discounts worth grabbing. In this article, you’ll find real-time pricing at all major retailers for Apple’s current lineup, and we’ve also highlighted some of the top discounts each week. Plus, for even more deals, we’ve linked to our dedicated deals round-ups for each product category. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Just be aware that Black Friday deals week is fast approaching at the end of November, at which point you can expect to see some of the best deals. Take a look at our <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/1375970/best-apple-black-friday-deals-2023.html\">Best Apple Black Friday Deals round-up</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Use the table of contents to jump to the best deals right now for the Apple product you want. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Best AirPods deals</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/airpods-pro2-hero.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"AirPods Pro 2\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/airpods-pro2-hero.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 5039w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/airpods-pro2-hero.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/airpods-pro2-hero.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/airpods-pro2-hero.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/airpods-pro2-hero.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/airpods-pro2-hero.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/airpods-pro2-hero.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/airpods-pro2-hero.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" /></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>U.S.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><span>Amazon, </span><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07PXGQC1Q/?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">AirPods (2nd gen): $99</a><span> ($30 off)</span></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Walmart, <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/321564/565706/9383?veh=aff&amp;sourceid=imp_000011112222333344&amp;u=https://www.walmart.com/ip/AirPods-Pro-2nd-generation-with-MagS