n<p>In the U.K., we do see Apple-certified resellers discount unlocked iPhones, although we aren’t yet seeing any really good deals on the new range of iPhones for 2023. We are recording the <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2075192/iphone-15-plus-pro-max-best-deals-carriers-uk.html\">best prices of iPhone 15 in the U.K.</a> separately. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is possible to find discounts on the now discontinued iPhone 14 Pro and Pro Max, and iPhone 13 mini, and older handsets, including the following deals, but remember Apple has reduced pricing in the U.K. for the new range of handsets, so the discounts may not be as good as they look: </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Box, <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=33021&amp;awinaffid=254429&amp;clickref=1-1-541154-1-0-0&amp;ued=https://www.box.co.uk/MTPD3ZDA-Open-Box-Apple-iPhone-15-512GB-Sim-Free-_4914763.html\" target=\"_blank\">iPhone 15, 512GB</a>, £989.10, £109 off </li>\n\n\n\n<li>John Lewis, <a href=\"https://john-lewis-and-partners.pxf.io/c/312327/871855/12148?subId1=1-1-541154-1-0-0&amp;u=https://www.johnlewis.com/apple-iphone-14-pro-max-ios-6-7-inch-5g-sim-free-128gb/gold/p6345523\" target=\"_blank\">iPhone 14 Pro Max:</a> £1,139 (£60 off, plus two-year warranty; RRP before being discontinued in fall 2023 was £1,199)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>John Lewis, <a href=\"https://john-lewis-and-partners.pxf.io/c/312327/871855/12148?subId1=1-1-541154-1-0-0&amp;u=https://www.johnlewis.com/apple-iphone-14-pro-ios-6-1-inch-5g-sim-free-128gb/silver/p6345519\" target=\"_blank\">iPhone 14 Pro:</a> £1,039 (£60 off, plus two-year warranty; RRP before being discontinued in fall 2023 was £1,099)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Amazon, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0BDJY2DFH?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">iPhone 14 Plus:</a> £749 (£50 off; RRP £799)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Amazon, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0BDJHR5DD?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" tar